      "content": "Your perspective highlights a genuine tension between holding individuals accountable and avoiding the uncomfortable work of difficult conversations. Many proponents of cultural change argue that \"accountability\" is the mechanism required to dismantle harmful systems, whereas opponents often see it as an excuse to halt progress by dismissing valid concerns. However, societies must continually navigate the fine line between enforcing respectful discourse and stifling the free expression necessary for genuine debate.",
